I understand your urgency, Dr. Smith, and I will ensure that your concerns are addressed promptly. However, I must inform you that even in an emergency, we must follow strict protocols to protect patient privacy and comply with HIPAA regulations. Verification is a necessary step to ensure the security of the patient's information.

I will escalate this to my supervisor immediately. Please hold on while I make this happen.

